">$1,095+</p>\r\n              <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm mb-6\">\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"mr-2\">✓</span>\r\n                  <span>All film screenings</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"mr-2\">✓</span>\r\n                  <span>Filmmaker events</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"mr-2\">✓</span>\r\n                  <span>Industry panels</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"mr-2\">✓</span>\r\n                  <span>Q&A sessions</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-600 to-red-600 text-white rounded-xl p-6\">\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2\">Music</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-4\">$995+</p>\r\n              <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm mb-6\">\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"mr-2\">✓</span>\r\n                  <span>All showcases</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"mr-2\">✓</span>\r\n                  <span>Day parties</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"mr-2\">✓</span>\r\n                  <span>Industry meetups</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"mr-2\">✓</span>\r\n                  <span>Venue access</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"mt-8 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-blue-200\">\r\n            <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\r\n              <strong>💰 Early Bird Pricing:</strong> Save up to $200 by purchasing your badge before February 7, 2026. \r\n              Student and senior discounts available.\r\n            </p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\r\n              <strong>🎟️ Wristbands:</strong> Free wristbands provide access to official day parties and select music venues. \r\n              Available for Austin locals and visitors.\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        <section class=\"mb-16\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 pb-4 border-b-2 border-orange-600\">\r\n            Navigating Austin During SXSW\r\n          </h2>\r\n          \r\n          <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-gray-200\">\r\n              <div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🏨</div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Accommodations</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\r\n                Book early! Hotels fill up fast and prices surge during SXSW. Consider downtown for walkability or neighborhoods \r\n                like South Congress, East Austin, or North Loop.\r\n              </p>\r\n              <a href=\"/blog/sxsw-2026-hotel-guide\" class=\"text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 font-medium text-sm\">\r\n                Hotel Guide →\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-gray-200\">\r\n              <div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🚗</div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Transportation</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\r\n                Downtown gets congested. Use rideshare, bike rentals, scooters, or Austin's public transportation. \r\n                Walking between venues is often fastest during peak hours.\r\n              </p>\r\n              <a href=\"/blog/sxsw-2026-transportation-tips\" class=\"text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 font-medium text-sm\">\r\n                Getting Around →\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-gray-200\">\r\n              <div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🍔</div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Food & Dining</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\r\n                Austin's food scene shines during SXSW. From food trucks to fine dining, BBQ to breakfast tacos. \r\n                Make reservations or expect long waits at popular spots.\r\n              </p>\r\n              <a href=\"/blog/sxsw-2026-dining-guide\" class=\"text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 font-medium text-sm\">\r\n                Dining Guide →\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        <section class=\"mb-16\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 pb-4 border-b-2 border-orange-600\">\r\n            SXSW Survival Tips\r\n          </h2>\r\n          \r\n          <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-yellow-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-orange-200\">\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">Pro Tips</h3>\r\n              <ul class=\"space-y-3\">\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"text-orange-600 text-xl mr-3\">👟</span>\r\n                  <div>\r\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">Wear comfortable shoes</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">You'll walk 10+ miles per day</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"text-orange-600 text-xl mr-3\">🔋</span>\r\n                  <div>\r\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">Portable charger is essential</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Your phone will die by noon</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"text-orange-600 text-xl mr-3\">📱</span>\r\n                  <div>\r\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">Download the SXSW app</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Plan your schedule and get real-time updates</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"text-orange-600 text-xl mr-3\">💧</span>\r\n                  <div>\r\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">Stay hydrated</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Austin weather can be unpredictable in March</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"text-orange-600 text-xl mr-3\">🎫</span>\r\n                  <div>\r\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">Badge up at will call early</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Avoid long lines during peak times</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-purple-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-blue-200\">\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">What to Expect</h3>\r\n              <ul class=\"space-y-3\">\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"text-blue-600 text-xl mr-3\">👥</span>\r\n                  <div>\r\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">Massive crowds</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">400K+ attendees fill downtown Austin</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"text-blue-600 text-xl mr-3\">⏰</span>\r\n                  <div>\r\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">Long lines</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Popular events fill up fast, arrive early</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"text-blue-600 text-xl mr-3\">🌡️</span>\r\n                  <div>\r\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">Variable weather</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Layer clothes and bring rain gear</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"text-blue-600 text-xl mr-3\">🎉</span>\r\n                  <div>\r\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">Serendipity moments</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Best experiences are often unplanned</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\r\n                  <span class=\"text-blue-600 text-xl mr-3\">😴</span>\r\n                  <div>\r\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-gray-900\">Exhaustion</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Events run from 11am to 2am daily</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        <section class=\"mb-16\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 pb-4 border-b-2 border-orange-600\">\r\n            SXSW's Impact on Austin\r\n          </h2>\r\n          \r\n          <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8 border-2 border-green-200\">\r\n            <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-6\">\r\n              <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                <p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2\">$280M+</p>\r\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">Economic Impact (2025)</p>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                <p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2\">400K+</p>\r\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">Total Attendees</p>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                <p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2\">3,000+</p>\r\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">Jobs Created</p>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n                <p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2\">100+</p>\r\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">Countries Represented</p>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-center\">\r\n              SXSW is one of Austin's biggest annual events, bringing massive economic benefits to local businesses, \r\n              hotels, restaurants, and the creative community. The festival has helped establish Austin as a global \r\n              destination for innovation and culture.\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        <section class=\"mb-16\">\r\n          <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-red-600 rounded-xl p-12 text-center text-white\">\r\n            <h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold mb-4\">Ready for SXSW 2026?</h2>\r\n            <p class=\"text-xl mb-8 text-orange-50\">\r\n              Join us in Austin this March for nine unforgettable days of music, film, and innovation\r\n            </p>\r\n            <div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4\">\r\n              <a \r\n                href=\"https://www.sxsw.com\" \r\n                target=\"_blank\"\r\n                class=\"inline-block bg-white text-orange-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors font-bold text-lg\"\r\n              >\r\n                Buy Badges →\r\n              </a>\r\n              <a \r\n                href=\"/blog?tag=sxsw\" \r\n                class=\"inline-block bg-yellow-500 text-gray-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-yellow-400 transition-colors font-bold text-lg\"\r\n              >\r\n                Read Our Coverage →\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        <section>\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 pb-4 border-b-2 border-orange-600\">\r\n            Related Coverage\r\n          </h2>\r\n          \r\n          <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\r\n            <a href=\"/blog?tag=austin\" class=\"bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 transition-colors\">\r\n              <p class=\"font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Austin News</p>\r\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Latest updates from Texas' capital city</p>\r\n            </a>\r\n            <a href=\"/blog?tag=tech-conferences\" class=\"bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 transition-colors\">\r\n              <p class=\"font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Tech Events</p>\r\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Major technology conferences and summits</p>\r\n            </a>\r\n            <a href=\"/blog?tag=music-festivals\" class=\"bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 transition-colors\">\r\n              <p class=\"font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Music Festivals</p>\r\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Coverage of major music events worldwide</p>\r\n            </a>\r\n            <a href=\"/blog?tag=film-festival